I was born Jewish, raised in a vrey reformed Jewish household, but Jewish nonetheless. We went to temple during high holy days and I beleived in God.<br>
I started not the beleive in God and went back and forth from being atheist to agnostic to God-beleiver and so on. I guess I wasn't really sure waht to beleive and didn't give it much thought for a while.<br>
Now, my grandmother is a devout Protestant. She's always been a very kind person and never intentionally tried to convert anyone. I was with her one day and asked her a question about the Bible. We talked for a few days until I finally decided that this was real, that Jesus was the Son of God.<br>
What made me beleive I suppose is seeing the Old Testament prophecies fulfilled, things that are common knowledge (he woulod be born in Bethlehem) and knowing that those weren't put in there after his death becase Jews use the same Old book <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
Even now I struggle from time to time with my beleifs. There has been a number of occassions when I've thought that perhaps Islam is the true religion (although I will always stand on how violent the Koran is, no I'm not bashing anyone here). It's something that's stressed me out a lot and even know I consider atheism as truth. However, in the end I always go back to  being Protestant, but who knows waht the future holds.<br>
A few days before Jesus died he said this: &quot;I leave you with these words: love one another.&quot; I do beleive in hell, and I also beleive in heaven, and I beleive that heaven is acheived by what Jesus said when he said &quot;I am the way the truth and the light, no one comes to the Father except by me.&quot; But even if you don't beleive in God, his words of &quot;love one another&quot; are something everyone should value, be they atheist, Hindu, pagan. Whether or not he was God, thats up to speculation. What isn't, I think most people would agree, is that the lesson of life he left with us is something that would benefit everyone (love, peace, happiness, etc., not talking about heaven/hell).<br>
Yeah, anyway thats my defining moment <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uareyoubackfriend.showPublicProfile?language=EN>areyoubackfriend</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/25/02 8:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=17.topic&index=344>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: bleh</span><hr size=1> What makes you think he said that? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uyoshamendel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>YoshaMendel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/25/02 10:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=17.topic&index=345>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/arvcondor/radioactivejewman.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: bleh</span><hr size=1> who said what, what the fuck are you talking about. and about the palestinian conflict, in your post you said it was about land yourself. stop bitching and then repeat what i just said. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uyoshamendel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>YoshaMendel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/25/02 10:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddRep